                        <p>General administration of the mails.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <dateline rendition="#left"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1874-08-21"><hi rend="italic">August</hi> 21,
